<section class="reviews mod book-content">
    <header>
        <a href="new_review" rel="nofollow" class="create-review redbutt rr" 
            data-isverify="False"
            data-verify-url="https://www.douban.com/accounts/phone/verify?redir=https://book.douban.com/subject/3361042/new_review">
            <span>我要写书评</span>
        </a>
        <h2>
            18世纪美洲和欧洲的革命的书评 · · · · · ·
            <span class="pl">(<a href="reviews">全部 1 条</a>)</span>
        </h2>
    </header>


        


<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="3710897">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3710897/" class="title-link">欧美18世纪的革命画卷</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3710897"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/12036924/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u12036924-79.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/12036924/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">紫檀</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-09-21"
      class="main-meta">2010-09-21 12:26:21</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3710897_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  想给大西洋两岸的三大洲梳理出革命的年谱，本身就是一件颇具革命念头的事件。18世纪的欧洲比较单纯，他们不计较土地和金钱，一个心眼去征服异己的文明。而美洲却支离破碎，各种革命主张日渐狰狞，美国的南北战争是民主的雏形，南美山高林密，适合打游击，一直打到今天

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/3710897/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 3没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_3710897_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_3710897_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










            <p class="pl" align="right">
                &gt;
                <a href="reviews">
                    更多书评1篇
                </a>
            </p>
